Logically speaking, we can not reuse this {color:#de350b}genesisBlock{color} .

 

_+let {color:#de350b}genesisBlock{color} = await this.proxy.getGenesisBlock(channelName);+_

 

Otherwise, nodes that do not join the channel will also be wrongly written to the database.

 

In addition, because proxy only gets the channel list from {color:#de350b}default{color} peer, there is a lack of channels that default peer does not join ({color:#de350b}other{color} nodes join). 

